summary: An ordinance relating to, and ratifying, approving and confirming the action of the Board of Public Works in entering into a contract with the Northern Pacific Railway Company on behalf of the City to cross, with a pipe line, the railroad right-of-way, of said company, in the north half of the southeast quarter of the southwest quarter of Section 9, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M., King County, Washington.
